<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
I think it's a little unreasonable to expect people to leave him up for a guild if he's not even your #1 target.  For better or worse this is a FFA server with a lot of spawn contention.  The best way to reserve a spawn is to hit that target on patch days.<br>
<br>
Having said that, in the case of Dozekar, there is no better time than the present for +CoV guilds to start bagging this guy.  He's about the only spawn with spectacular loots (granted not dropping directly) that lives for days after a patch.  After all once one +CoV guild kills him, I would venture to guess he'll be dying every patch day too.  When that day comes I guarantee the +CoV guilds won't be worried about the -all guilds - they will be groaning about the competition between themselves for Doz. <p>Reila / Ciryon<br>
60 Cleric / Enchanter<br>
Vea Victis / Ayonae Ro<br>
