<br>
It has more to do with the nature of what you are asking Palimax. It isn't, 'Let us have a shot at Doze', it is 'Please leave Doze up til we can get around to doing him'. These are very different things. Right now, he is always up on patch day and usually for days after that. Basically, I'd say if he isn't dead with a day of patch day, there is very little reason for complaint if someone else takes him, no matter what faction they are. We don't do calendars on this server, and that is basically what you are asking for here really. If you want Doze, just kill him if you can. But don't complain when he isn't up on Saturday when the servers were patched on Tuesday. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4380>Qaman</a><BR>
Sorcerer - Eternal Wrath<BR>
